JIRA Core 7.x Plugin SDK example : Creating workflow extensions
https://developer.atlassian.com/jiradev/jira-platform/guides/workflow/tutorial-creating-workflow-extensions

- SDK 6.2.4
- Intellj 14
- JIRA Software 7.1.4

If you want to run this on other JIRA Application such like JIRA ServiceDesk,  edit pom.xml to add following
<application>
	<applicationKey>jira-servicedesk</applicationKey>
	<version>${jira.servicedesk.application.version}</version>
</application>
.....
<properties>
.....
	<jira.servicedesk.application.version>7.1.4</jira.servicedesk.application.version>
.....
</properties>	

[Additional Info:]
You need 
- some icon files in src/main/resources/images/
- 2 exported Workflow files in src/main/resources/wfb
- MyProjectTemplate.soy in src/main/resources/soy

